0compute.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20deal%2C%20Microsoft%20will%20invest%20up%20to%20%245%20billion%20in%20Anthropic.%20Nvidia%2C%20whose%20chips%20are%20at%20the%20certain%20of%20this%20deal%20and%20many%20like%2C%20also%20agreed%20to%20invest%20up%20to%20%2410%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20spenders%20are%20created%20alike%2C%20either.%20OpenAI%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20in%20the%20red%20by%20%249%20billion%20this%20year%2C%20has%20about%20%241.4%20trillion%20in%20spending%20commitments%20for%20AI%20data%20centers%20over%20the%20next%20decade.%20Unlike%20Google%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20Microsoft%2C%20OpenAI%20doesn't%20have%20an%20established%20revenue%20base%20to%20fall%20back%20on%2C%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20why%20OpenAI%20CFO%20Sarah%20Friar%20sparked%20a%20brief%20firestorm%20when%20she%20appeared%20to%20suggest%20that%20the%20startup%20would%20want%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20government%20bailout%20to%20backstop%20its%20data%20center%20bets.%20Friar%20walked%20back%20her%20remarks%2C%20and%20Altman%20later%20emphasized%20that%20OpenAI%20didn't%20believe%20in%20bailouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227832%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Google%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F694881e464858d02d21737e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225221%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECheng%20Xin%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c9b3720d-f181-4552-a28b-4e64ae9a1a41%5C%22%3EGoogle%20gains%20an%20upper%20hand%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20has%20led%20much%20of%20the%20AI-model%20race%20since%20the%20release%20of%20ChatGPT%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20later%2C%20it%20was%20Altman%20who%20declared%20a%20%26quot%3Bcode%20red%2C%26quot%3B%20just%20over%20a%20month%20after%20OpenAI%20completed%20its%20corporate%20restructuring%2C%20aimed%20at%20giving%20it%20more%20freedom%20to%20raise%20money%20to%20fund%20its%20AI%20advancements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C