ical%20Conversation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%20answers%20your%20relationship%20and%20money%20questions.%20Looking%20for%20advice%20on%20how%20your%20savings%2C%20debt%2C%20or%20another%20financial%20challenge%20is%20affecting%20your%20relationships%3F%20Submit%20your%20question%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdhFnAxR57cNtGiwNUd-6vLAYAc75grvly3C10-854vFP4arw%2Fviewform%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20Google%20form%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EDear%20Longing%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can%20empathize%20with%20both%20you%20and%20your%20husband.%20On%20one%20hand%2C%20your%20husband%20is%20indignant%20over%20the%20high%20cost%20of%20groceries%20these%20days%20%E2%80%94%20a%20grudge%20I%20also%20can't%20seem%20to%20shake.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20I%20feel%20your%20pain.%20Trying%20to%20explain%20to%20someone%20still%20emotionally%20stuck%20in%202005%20%E2%80%94%20when%20a%20carton%20of%20eggs%20and%20a%20loaf%20of%20bread%20were%20just%20over%20a%20dollar%20each%20%E2%80%94%20that%20grocery%20costs%20not%20only%20rose%20steadily%20over%20the%20years%20but%20then%20skyrocketed%20during%20the%20pandemic%20is%20the%20pinnacle%20of%20domestic%20frustration.%20I%20say%20that%20because%20for%20your%20husband%20to%20emotionally%20exist%20in%202005%2C%20twenty%20years%20after%20the%20fact%2C%20means%20he%20must%20have%20been%20closing%20his%20eyes%2C%20putting%20his%20hands%20over%20his%20ears%2C%20and%20screaming%2C%20%26quot%3BLa%2C%20la%2C%20la%2C%20I'm%20not%20listening.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20you%20alone%20have%20been%20covering%20grocery%20shopping%20for%20your%20entire%20family%2C%20on%20pain%20of%20his%20childish%20antics%20getting%20even%20louder%20should%20he%20see%20the%20prices%20for%20himself.%20And%20the%20only%20thanks%20you%20get%20for%20carrying%20this%20significant%20chunk%20of%20household%20responsibility%20alone%20is%20him%20periodically%20telling%20you%20that%20you%20must%20be%20doing%20it%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20husband's%20ignorance%20seems%20a%20bit%20willful.%20He%20agrees%20you%20need%20higher-quality%20%E2%80%94%20and%20therefore%2C%20higher-priced%20%E2%80%94%20groceries.%20Yet%20he%20seems%20unwilling%20to%20shell%20out%20the%20money%20to%20pay%20for%20these%20necessary%20items.%20What's%20more%2C%20your%20husband%20makes%20a%20high%20six-figure%20income.%20No%20matter%20how%20unfair%20the%20current%20prices%20may%20feel%2C%20your%20husband%20knows%20he%20can%20afford%20a%20%249%20gallon%20of%20organic%20milk.%20(Full%20disclosure%3A%20I%20had%20to%20Google%20that%20price%2C%20and%20when%20I%20saw%20it%2C%20my%20stomach%20flipped.%20But%20this%20is%20the%20world%20we're%20all%20living%20in%20%E2%80%94%20including%20your%20husband%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20hard%20he%20tries%20to%20deny%20it.)%20However%2C%20as%20my%20kneejerk%20response%20to%20that%20price%20tag%20illustrates%2C%20understanding%20something%20and%20accepting%20it%20are%20two%20different%20propositions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20said%20you%20long%20to%20have%20logical%20conversations%20with%20your%20husband%20about%20food%20costs%3B%20that%20%26quot%3Blogic%26quot%3B%20you%20mention%20is%20the%20crux%20of%20the%20matter.%20The%20only%20way%20to%20free%20yourself%20of%20ugly%20afternoon%20spats%20over%20the%20cost%20of%20food%20%E2%80%94%20something%20your%20husband%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20realize%20is%20outside%20your%20control%20%E2%80%94%20is%20to%20get%20him%20out%20of%20his%20feelings%20of%20injustice%20and%20into%20a%20place%20of%20rational%20and%20functional%20tolerance%20for%20grocery%20store%20pricing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUp%20to%20now%2C%20you've%20tried%20to%20avoid%20these%20issues%20by%20protecting%20him%20from%20the%20reality%20of%20inflation%20and%20taking%20on%20all%20the%20sticker%20shock%20for%20both%20of%20you.%20Unfortunately%2C%20this%20plan%20was%20never%20bound%20for%20long-term%20success%20because%20sharing%20finances%20well%20requires%20everyone%20to%20be%20on%20the%20same%20page.%20One%20person%20can't%20remain%20blissfully%20ignorant%20while%20the%20other%20faces%20reality%20for%20both%20of%20them%20because%20shared%20finances%20mean%20shared%20outcomes%2C%20even%20when%20that%20outcome%20is%20just%20a%20gutting%20line%20item%20on%20the%20bank%20statements.%20Neither%20party%20can%20blame%20the%20other%20if%20they%20both%20understand%20the%20reality%20that%20led%20to%20that%20line%20item.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20hard%20as%20it%20may%20seem%2C%20the%20only%20way%20to%20get%20to%20the%20point%20of%20logically%20working%20through%20the%20realities%20of%20life%20together%20is%20to%20stop%20protecting%20him%20from%20them.%20He%20must%20be%20flung%20into%20the%20deep%20end%20of%20facts%2C%20forced%20to%20sink%20or%20swim.%20Faced%20with%20this%20choice%2C%20he%20won't%20have%20the%20space%20to%20stew%20in%20his%20feelings%20of%20injustice%20or%20nostalgia%20for%20the%20prices%20of%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20if%20your%20husband%20is%20so%20convinced%20you're%20grocery%20shopping%20wrong%2C%20it%20sounds%20like%20he%20needs%20to%20show%20you%20how%20it's%20done.%20And%20not%20just%20once%20or%20twice%3B%20he%20needs%20to%20take%20on%20grocery%20shopping%20responsibilities%20long%20enough%20to%20see%20the%20price%20of%20berries%20goes%20up%20when%20they're%20not%20in%20season%2C%20the%20fluctuations%20that%20accompany%20the%20holidays%2C%20the%20way%20you%20have%20to%20spend%20more%20during%20birthday%20celebrations%20or%20when%20family%20is%20in%20town%2C%20and%20see%20how%20his%20body%20fluctuates%20when%20he%20chooses%20wealth%20over%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20this%20shift%20will%20be%20far%20from%20easy.%20You've%20had%20a%20working%20system%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20and%20changing%20the%20personality%20behind%20your%20family's%20grocery%20shopping%20will%20have%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20all%20of%20you.%20As%20the%20expert%20on%20doing%20the%20job%20right%2C%20you'll%20likely%20face%20the%20most%20discomfort.%20This%20isn't%20to%20say%20that%20you%20should%20withhold%20your%20support%20and%20treat%20this%20like%20a%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20your%20husband%20needs%20to%20take%20accountability%20for%20not%20only%20his%20lack%20of%20involvement%20in%20such%20an%20essential%20task%20as%20feeding%20your%20family%2C%20but%20also%20his%20negative%2C%20unhelpful%20attitude%20when%20you've%20carried%20the%20weight%20of%20this%20responsibility.%20Any%20negative%20outcomes%20your%20husband%20encounters%20will%20serve%20as%20learning%20opportunities%2C%20and%20hopefully%2C%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20his%20learning%20lies%20transparency%2C%20respect%2C%20and%20logical%20conversation.%20And%20if%20your%20husband%20discovers%20helpful%20tips%20or%20life%20hacks%20that%20can%20help%20your%20family%20shop%20for%20groceries%20more%20frugally%20while%20maintaining%20the%20quality%20of%20food%20you%20need%2C%20that%20will%20benefit%20all%20of%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20you've%20borne%20the%20brunt%20of%20this%20task%20for%20two%20decades.%20At%20a%20bare%20minimum%2C%20you%20shouldn't%20be%20harangued%20for%20your%20methods.%20However%2C%20what%20you%20really%20deserve%20is%20an%20equal%20partner%20who%20recognizes%20and%20shares%20the%20burden%20of%20the%20realities%20of%20your%20lives.%20Hopefully%2C%20giving%20your%20husband%20a%20turn%20driving%20the%20grocery%20cart%20will%20accomplish%20all%20of%20the%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERooting%20for%20you%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELooking%20for%20advice%20on%20how%20your%20savings%2C%20debt%2C%20or%20another%20financial%20challenge%20is%20affecting%20your%20relationships%3F%20Write%20to%20For%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%20using%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdhFnAxR57cN