E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThree%20California%20teenagers%20created%20text-to-speech%20smart%20glasses%20powered%20by%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20wearable%20tech%20helps%20visually%20impaired%20students%20access%20reading%20materials.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAkhil%20Nagori%2C%20Evann%20Sun%2C%20and%20Lucas%20Yen's%20prototype%20won%20a%20%2410%2C000%20prize%20at%20a%20top%20science%20competition.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20companies%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20are%20raising%20billions%20to%20develop%20wearable%20AI-powered%20products.%20A%20trio%20of%20teenagers%20in%20nearby%20Santa%20Clara%20built%20theirs%20for%20less%20than%20%24100.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAkhil%20Nagori%2C%20Evann%20Sun%2C%20and%20Lucas%20Shengwen%20Yen%2C%20all%20of%20them%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E15%20years%20old%2C%20invented%20wearable%20glasses%20powered%20by%20AI%20that%20translate%20text%20to%20speech%20in%20real%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20main%20goal%20was%20to%20create%20an%20easy%2C%20cost-efficient%20way%20to%20transcribe%20text%20from%20any%20format%20for%20visually%20impaired%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20Nagori%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENagori%2C%20Sun%2C%20and%20Yen%20submitted%20their%20prototype%2C%20which%20took%20about%20five%20months%20to%20complete%2C%20to%20the%20Thermo%20Fisher%20Scientific%20Junior%20Innovators%20Challenge%20in%20October%20and%20won%20a%20%2410%2C000%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221742%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22AI-powered%20glasses%20created%20by%20Akhil%20Nagori%2C%20Evann%20Sun%2C%20and%20%20Lucas%20Shengwen%20Yen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6948761d04eda4732f2df10e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22980%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBuilding%20the%20glasses%20took%20Akhil%20Nagori%2C%20Evann%20Sun%2C%20and%20Lucas%20Shengwen%20Yen%20about%20five%20months.%3Cp%3EAkhil%20Nagori%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20boys%20said%20their%20prototype%20has%20over%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E90%25%20accuracy%20when%20translating%20text%20to%20speech.%20The%20glasses%20are%20designed%20to%20take%20pictures%2C%20extract%20the%20text%2C%20and%20convert%20the%20text%20to%20audio%20played%20through%20tiny%20speakers%20built%20into%20the%20glasses%20frames.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20most%20important%20aspects%20of%20our%20project%20is%20the%20load%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Yen%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20averaged%20around%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E13%20seconds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20to%20build%20AI-powered%20text-to-speech%20glasses%20came%20after%20Nagori%20traveled%20to%20India%20to%20visit%20family%2C%20including%20his%20great-uncle%20who%20is%20visually%20impaired%20and%20works%20as%20a%20cashier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20all%20these%20boxes%20filled%20with%20these%20braille%20receipts.%20He%20has%20to%20go%20through%20them%20line%20by%20line%2C%26quot%3B%20Nagori%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20saw%20that%2C%20I%20said%2C%20'There's%20got%20to%20be%20an%20easier%20way%20that's%20not%20so%20tedious.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2213898e79-41d5-40e7-8755-b066f97c282f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESun%2C%20Nagori%2C%20and%20Yen%20used%20800%20images%20to%20train%20their%20software%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20create%20the%20glasses%2C%20the%20boys%20had%20to%20clear%20three%20hurdles%3A%20hardware%2C%20software%2C%20and%20collecting%20data%20through%20testing.%20Sun%20said%20they%20designed%20the%20glasses%20frames%20with%20Fusion%20360%2C%20a%20CAD%20software%2C%20and%20used%20a%203D%20printer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20found%20the%20average%20glasses%20dimensions%20for%20middle%20to%20high%20school%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20Sun%20said.%20%26quot%3BSince%20we're%20trying%20to%20have%20all%20of%20the%20components%20on%20the%20glasses%2C%20we%20had%20to%20custom-design%20the%20areas%20for%20all%20of%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20glasses%20contain%20a%20camera%2C%20battery%2C%20speakers%2C%20and%20a%20small%20computer%20board%20called%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fraspberry-pi-launches-5-pi-zero-computer-2015-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERaspberry%20Pi%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20also%20have%20a%20tiny%20on-and-off%20switch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20students%20to%20use%20this%20for%2C%20give%20or%20take%2C%20the%20entire%20school%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Sun%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20really%20concerned%20about%20the%20battery%20life%2C%20especially%20when%20we%20are%20using%20such%20a%20small%20battery.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20software%2C%20Nagori%20said%20they%20custom-trained%20a%20convolutional%20recurrent%20neural%20network%2C%20or%20CRNN%2C%20on%20a%20dataset%20of%20800%20images%20collected%20from%20school%20textbooks%20and%20other%20education%20materials.%20They%20ensured%20that%20the%20model%20was%20trained%20on%20colorful%20images%20and%20different%20types%20of%20fonts%2C%20which%20are%20often%20characteristic%20of%20textbooks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Akhil%20Nagori%20is%20wearing%20AI-powered%20text-to-speech%20glasses.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6948758e04eda4732f2df10b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAkhil%20Nagori%20wears%20a%20prototype%20of%20their%20AI-powered%20glasses.%3Cp%3EAkhil%20Nagori%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20to%20take%20those%20images%20ourselves%20in%20three%20different%20lighting%20conditions%20that%20mimicked%20classroom%2C%20low%20lighting%2C%20and%20outdoor%20lighting%2C%26quot%3B%20Nagori%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECollecting%20data%20on%20their%20prototype%20involved%20conducting%20many%20test%20rounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20all%20our%20hardware%20and%20software%20were%20done%2C%20we%20tested%20our%20software%20part%2C%26quot%3B%20Sun%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20would%20input%20images%20that%20we%20saw%20online%20or%20that%20we%20took%20ourselves%20into%20our%20software%20model.%20Then%2C%20it%20extracted%20the%20text%20and%20gave%20us%20an%20MP3%20file%2C%20which%20we%20could%20use%20to%20improve%20our%20accuracy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENagori%2C%20Sun%2C%20and%20Yen's%20prototype%20ultimately%20gained%20national%20recognition%2C%20but%20their%20journey%20wasn't%20without%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20all-nighters%2C%26quot%3B%20Nagori%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20Yen%20said%20the%20glasses%20underwent%20a%20serious%20defect%20hours%20before%20they%20were%20scheduled%20to%20present%20the%20prototype%20at%20the%20science%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20flight%20there%2C%20some%20of%20our%20soldering%20came%20off%20the%20Raspberry%20Pi.%20Without%20the%20soldering%2C%20nothing%20worked%2C%20and%20the%20glasses%20wouldn't%20start%20up.%20We%20were%20all%20in%20panic%20mode%2C%26quot%3B%20Yen%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20night%20before%20we%20were%20presenting%2C%20my%20dad%20ran%20to%20the%20closest%20mechanic%20store%20and%20got%20a%20soldering%20iron.%20The%20three%20of%20us%20put%20on%20masks%2C%20hunched%20over%2C%20and%20fixed%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ec47fc40-ab18-4c10-9d7d-8201542bf9d5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EScaling%20up%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Thermo%20Fisher%20Scientific%20Junior%20Innovators%20Challenge%20is%20a%20top%20STEM%20research%20competition%20for%20students%2C%20so%20receiving%20recognition%20is%20a%20notable%20achievement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20qualify%2C%20middle%20school%20students%20must%20compete%20at%20a%20local%20science%20or%20engineering%20fair%2C%20where%20judges%20nominate%20the%20top%2010%25%20of%20projects.%20About%202%2C000%20of%20those%20winners%20apply%20to%20compete%20at%20the%20national%20competition%2C%20but%20only%20300%20are%20selected.%20From%20there%2C%20judges%20whittle%20the%20number%20down%20to%2030%20applicants%2C%20who%20present%20their%20research%20and%20complete%20challenges%20in%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Akhil%20Nagori%20and%20Evann%20Sun%20at%20the%20Thermo%20Fisher%20Scientific%20Junior%20Innovators%20Challenge.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F694873cb64858d02d21737c8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222730%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAkhil%20Nagori%20and%20Evann%20Sun%20won%20awards%20at%20the%20Thermo%20Fisher%20Scientific%20Leadership%20Award.%3Cp%3ESociety%20for%20Science%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20%2410%2C000%20prize%20the%20boys%20won%20for%20the%20glasses%2C%20Nagori%20also%20earned%20the%20Thermo%20Fisher%20Scientific%20Leadership%20Award.%20Sun%20received%20%2410%2C000%20for%20the%20Lemelson%20Foundation%20Award%20for%20Invention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWinning%20at%20the%20competition%20meant%20a%20lot%20to%20Nagori%2C%20Sun%2C%20and%20Yen%2C%20who%20initially%20didn't%20receive%20a%20nomination.%20However%2C%20judges%20from%20the%20state%20level%20attended%20the%20boys'%20competition%20and%20recognized%20the%20value%20in%20their%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20really%20taught%20us%20that%20even%20if%20we%20don't%20get%20what%20we%20want%20the%20first%20time%2C%20as%20long%20as%20we%20work%20hard%20and%20stay%20committed%2C%20we%20can%20come%20back%20and%20be%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20Sun%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20research%20is%20still%20in%20the%20prototype%20phase%2C%20but%20they%20have%20ambitious%20plans%20to%20expand.%20Nagori%20said%20they%20received%20a%20%24%2C5000%20grant%20to%20scale%20their%20glasses%2C%20which%20will%20help%20them%20reach%20more%20of%20their%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20currently%20working%20on%20implementing%20a%20lot%20of%20our%20glasses%20throughout%20California%2C%26quot%3