D%5C%22%5C%22%3Equalify%20for%20Medicaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20they%20have%20limited%20assets%20and%20low%20incomes%2C%20though%20receiving%20benefits%20has%20sometimes%20come%20at%20a%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20created%20a%20demoralizing%20situation%2C%20because%20if%20you%20have%20the%20money%2C%20you%20have%20to%20spend%20it%20on%20long-term%20care%2C%20which%20is%20super%20expensive.%20If%20you%20don't%20have%20the%20money%2C%20then%20your%20life%20quality%20is%20going%20to%20suffer%2C%20but%20you're%20fully%20admitted%20into%20the%20long-term%20care%20facilities%20run%20by%20the%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mo%20Wang%2C%20a%20distinguished%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Florida's%20Warrington%20College%20of%20Business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20likely%20that%20many%20of%20the%20over%207%20million%20low-income%20older%20Americans%20could%20have%20their%20benefits%20cut%2C%20burdening%20people%20needing%20nursing%20facility%20care%20or%20facing%20out-of-pocket%20medical%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMedicare%20premiums%20will%20also%20rise%20next%20year.%20Rising%20healthcare%20costs%20will%20push%20the%20monthly%20Medicare%20Part%20B%20premium%20up%20nearly%2010%25%20to%20%24203%2C%20which%20will%20eat%20into%20Social%20Security%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20get%20Social%20Security%2C%20they%20give%20you%20a%203%25%20raise%2C%20and%20then%20Medicare%20takes%20a%20good%20portion%20of%20that%20because%20Medicare%20rates%20also%20increase%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Vince%20Scidone%2C%2091.%20%26quot%3BThat%203%25%20is%20not%20really%20a%203%25%20raise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f0c5c204-20cc-4cfe-920f-1ac583153149%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20difficult%20job%20market%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOlder%20Americans%20comprise%20the%20fastest-growing%20demographic%20in%20the%20workforce.%20Nearly%20550%2C000%20Americans%2080%20and%20older%20work%20at%20least%20part-time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20lab