_index%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Gul%20Jaipur%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20production%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20issue%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ananya%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20challenge%20is%20timelines.%20Because%20this%20trend%20is%20still%20new%2C%20couples%20often%20place%20orders%20just%20a%20week%20before%20the%20wedding.%20Customisation%20takes%20time%2C%20and%20since%20it%E2%80%99s%20for%20their%20special%20day%2C%20it%20has%20to%20be%20absolutely%20perfect.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20sentiment%2C%20Ananya%20also%20points%20to%20the%20sustainability%20argument.%20Fresh%20flowers%20often%20travel%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20India%20or%20even%20internationally%2C%20requiring%20refrigeration%20and%20transport.%20Crochet%20alternatives%2C%20she%20says%2C%20cut%20down%20this%20carbon%20footprint%20significantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20better%20way%20forward.%20Fresh%20flowers%20end%20up%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F449690%2Fdelhi-zero-waste-colony-navjivan-vihar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egarbage%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewithin%20hours.%20Crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecan%20be%20priced%20in%20the%20same%20range%2C%20and%20you%20can%20keep%20them%20forever%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20lockdown%20hobby%20turns%20into%20forever%20memories%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%2018-year-old%20Manya%20Jain%20of%20Knot%20Kisses%2C%20the%20journey%20to%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebegan%20in%20her%20bedroom%20during%20the%202020%20lockdown.%20She%20was%20barely%2013%20when%20she%20picked%20up%20a%20hook%20because%20she%20wanted%20new%20clothes%20and%20her%20mother%20refused%20to%20buy%20them.%20What%20started%20as%20a%20rebellion%20became%20a%20craft%2C%20and%20then%20a%20calling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E